Project Title

AI-Based Employee Attendance and Salary Management System

Problem Statement

Managing employee attendance and salary records manually is time-consuming and prone to errors. Organizations often face challenges in tracking attendance, calculating salaries, managing leave records, and generating payroll reports accurately. An AI-Based Employee Attendance and Salary Management System automates these processes, improving efficiency, accuracy, and transparency.

Objectives

- To automate employee attendance tracking.
- To manage employee records efficiently.
- To automate salary calculation based on attendance data.
- To maintain leave and payroll records.
- To reduce manual errors and administrative workload.
- To provide AI-based insights and reports for management.

Modules

1. Employee Management

- Employee registration
- Employee profile management
- Employee record maintenance

2. Attendance Management

- Daily attendance recording
- Attendance tracking and monitoring
- Attendance history management

3. Salary Management

- Automatic salary calculation
- Payroll generation
- Salary slip generation

4. Leave Management

- Leave application
- Leave approval/rejection
- Leave record maintenance

5. AI Analytics Module

- Attendance pattern analysis
- Employee performance insights
- Automated report generation

6. Reports Module

- Attendance reports
- Salary reports
- Employee performance reports

Database Tables

Table Name   Description
Employees    Stores employee details
Attendance   Stores attendance records
Salary       Stores salary information
Leave        Stores leave details
Payroll      Stores payroll records
Users        Stores login credentials
Reports      Stores generated reports

Technologies Used

Component   Technology
Front       End HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript
Back End    Java (Spring Boot)
Database    MySQL
IDE         VS Code / IntelliJ IDEA
AI Module   Machine Learning (Optional)

Expected Outcome

The system provides an efficient way to manage employee attendance and salary processes, reduces paperwork, improves record accuracy, automates payroll generation, and enhances organizational productivity through AI-based analysis and reporting.
